      "text": "Before you speak, it speaks for you. \nBefore you enter a room, it arrives ahead of you. \nBefore you pitch an idea or launch a product or ask\nfor a raise, your aura has already negotiated the\nterms. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
