      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "And here's where... People fail. \nThey try to fake confidence. \nThey paste on smiles. \nThey rehearse affirmations they don't believe. \nThey act as if but vibrate fear underneath it all. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "X9UuW9544nuiWS47FVOD6",
      "originalText": "And here's where... People fail. \nThey try to fake confidence. \nThey paste on smiles. \nThey rehearse affirmations they don't believe. \nThey act as if but vibrate fear underneath it all. ",
