      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775007209312,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "And if you hold these beliefs, no matter\nhow small, you are repelling the very thing\nyou say you want. \n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "isYvTz7Q4c3-LhnozYJWp",
      "originalText": "And if you hold these beliefs, no matter how small, you are repelling the very thing you say you want. \n",
