      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "This is why so many lottery winners go broke. \nTheir vibration didn't match the money. \nTheir aura was still one of fear, confusion, and limitation. \nAnd so the money had to leave because energy seeks\nalignment. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
