      "text": "Even if your account says zero, \ncan you walk with your head high? \nCan you speak your truth boldly? \nCan you act like someone who knows their worth without\napology? ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
