      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "You walk into a room and people feel it. \nYou speak and people listen.\nYou ask and doors open. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "GZzq2N-vN0RGibv5wN7MM",
      "originalText": "You walk into a room and people feel it. \nYou speak and people listen.\nYou ask and doors open. ",
