      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Kkcku_Uu9bfuCuSTY_vCl",
      "originalText": "It is shaped by every thought, word, and action. \nYou are always training it, consciously or unconsciously. \nSo train it with intent.",
