      "text": "If you doubt yourself, and you're surrounded by\ncomplainers, gossipers, and critics, your self-doubt will\nmultiply.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "CoJ7sPYH36oFXwDpSYz3D",
      "originalText": "If you doubt yourself, and you're surrounded by complainers, gossipers, and critics, your self-doubt will multiply.",
