      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774833833843,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "They speak what they believe. \nThey act how they feel. \nThey move as if it's already real. \nThat level of congruence creates power. \nIt creates certainty. \nIt creates trust. \nOthers feel it, and they want to align. \nThey want to support you, buy from you, invest\nin you. \nNot because of what you said, but because of\nhow your presence made them feel.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "aWUncf72gRGIadiptiAsG",
      "originalText": "They speak what they believe. \nThey act how they feel. \nThey move as if it's already real. \nThat level of congruence creates power. \nIt creates certainty. \nIt creates trust. \nOthers feel it, and they want to align. \nThey want to support you, buy from you, invest in you. \nNot because of what you said, but because of how your presence made them feel.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
