      "text": "Release it. Let your old self die. \nBecause the person you're becoming cannot grow\ninside the shell of the person you were. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "N4FsunaBRW5sV2HpqoCBR",
      "originalText": "Release it. Let your old self die. \nBecause the person you're becoming cannot grow inside the shell of the person you were. ",
