      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Because you finally decided to live as who you are,\nnot who they remember. \nAnd that courage, that audacity, is what\nstrengthens your aura more than any technique or\ntool.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "EWRpi9qO-wnZA76muPxm0",
      "originalText": "Because you finally decided to live as who you are, not who they remember. \nAnd that courage, that audacity, is what strengthens your aura more than any technique or tool.",
