      "updated": 1775007029095,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Every morning before the noise of the world creeps in. \nBefore the phone rings. \nBefore the headlines. \nBefore the... Sit with yourself. \nFive minutes. \nThat's all. Close your eyes. \nTake three deep breaths. And visualize your aura glowing,\nbrighter, stronger, expanding around you. \nNow speak to it. Command it. \nSay, I am a magnet for abundance. \nSay, my presence is wealth. \nSay money is safe with me. \nSuccess flows to me. \nI am aligned with expansion. \nFeel these words not as fantasy, but as truth. \nPractice that feeling until your body believes it. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Ob51NewrETVn0nOcoEPRi",
      "originalText": "Every morning before the noise of the world creeps in. \nBefore the phone rings. \nBefore the headlines. \nBefore the... Sit with yourself. \nFive minutes. \nThat's all. Close your eyes. \nTake three deep breaths. And visualize your aura glowing, brighter, stronger, expanding around you. \nNow speak to it. Command it. \nSay, I am a magnet for abundance. \nSay, my presence is wealth. \nSay money is safe with me. \nSuccess flows to me. \nI am aligned with expansion. \nFeel these words not as fantasy, but as truth. \nPractice that feeling until your body believes it. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
