      "updated": 1774972075725,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "If you wait to feel ready before you act, you will\nnever act. \nIf you wait to be validated before you speak, you\nwill never speak. \nIf you wait to be chosen before you commit, you\nwill live in permanent hesitation. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "wdDj2sYc2E9xAHZAfpbDb",
      "originalText": "If you wait to feel ready before you act, you will never act. \nIf you wait to be validated before you speak, you will never speak. \nIf you wait to be chosen before you commit, you will live in permanent hesitation. ",
