      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775007470662,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "That's one. \nEmotional audit. \nEvery morning, ask yourself, what am I feeling, and does\nit serve the person I'm becoming? \nIf the answer is no, reframe it. \nDon't let an unqualified emotion run your day. \nInterrupt it. Replace it. Realign. \n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "exxDBbb4kOmRTHpiRUaAB",
      "originalText": "That's one. \nEmotional audit. \nEvery morning, ask yourself, what am I feeling, and does it serve the person I'm becoming? \nIf the answer is no, reframe it. \nDon't let an unqualified emotion run your day. \nInterrupt it. Replace it. Realign. \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
