      "originalText": "Three, visualization repetition. \nClose your eyes. \nFeel your future self. \nNot from the outside looking in, but from the inside out. \nSee through his eyes. Move with his posture. \nSmile with this certainty. \nMake that identity so familiar that your body begins to adopt it as its own.",
